  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Toss the padron peppers with olive oil, salt, and black pepper on a baking sheet.",
    "Roast the peppers in the oven for 15 minutes, or until slightly charred.",
    "Toast the whole wheat bread until lightly browned.",
    "Spread a layer of vegan mayonnaise on each toasted bread slice.",
    "Top each bread slice with a roasted padron pepper.",
    "Drizzle malt syrup over the peppers.",
    "Sprinkle chopped parsley over the top.",
    "Serve in a bento-box vessel immediately."
